#: ../tex-templates-utbm-phdthesis.templates:1001
msgid "Agreement for the Report Template of the UTBM"
msgstr "Licence d'utilisation pour le patron de rapport pour l'UTBM"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2019.templates:1001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2021.templates:1001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2025.templates:1001
#: ../tex-templates-utbm-phdthesis.templates:1001
#: ../tex-templates-ube-phdthesis.templates:1001
#: ../tex-templates-spimhdr.templates:1001
msgid ""
"THE ACCOMPANYING TEMPLATE IS PROVIDED UNDER THE TERMS OF THIS LICENSE "
"AGREEMENT. ANY USE, REPRODUCTION OR DISTRIBUTION OF THE EXTENSION "
"CONSTITUTES RECIPIENT'S ACCEPTANCE OF THIS AGREEMENT."
msgstr ""
"LE PATRON ACCOMPAGNANT CE PAQUET EST FOURNI SOUS LES TERMES DE CETTE LICENCE "
"D'UTILISATION. TOUT USAGE, REPRODUCTION OU DISTRIBUTION DE CE PATRON "
"IMPLIQUE L'ACCEPTATION IMPLICITE DE CETTE LICENCE."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2019.templates:1001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2021.templates:1001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2025.templates:1001
#: ../tex-templates-utbm-phdthesis.templates:1001
msgid ""
"YOU ARE GRANTED TO USE, REPRODUCE OR DISTRIBUTE THE UTBM TEMPLATE  LATEX "
"PACKAGE IF AND ONLY IF: A) YOU ARE A REGISTERED MEMBER OF THE UNIVERSITE DE "
"TECHNOLOGIE DE BELFORT-MONTBELIARD, OR B) YOU ARE OFFICIALLY AND EXPLICITELY "
"AUTHORIZED TO USE THIS EXTENSION BY A REPRESENTATIVE OF THE UNIVERSITE DE "
"TECHNOLOGIE DE BELFORT-MONTBELIARD."
msgstr ""
"VOUS ETES AUTORISE A UTILISE, REPRODUIRE OU DISTRIBUER LE PATRON LATEX DE "
"L'UTBM SI ET SEULEMENT SI : A) VOUS ETES OFFICIELLEMENT MEMBRE DE "
"L'UNIVERSITE DE TECHNOLOGIE DE BELFORT-MONTBELIARD, OU B) VOUS ETES "
"OFFICIELLEMENT AUTORISE POUR L'USAGE DE CE PATRON PAR UN REPRESENTANT "
"OFFICIEL DE L'UNIVERSITE DE TECHNOLOGIE DE BELFORT-MONTBELIARD."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2019.templates:2001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2021.templates:2001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2025.templates:2001
#: ../tex-templates-utbm-phdthesis.templates:2001
msgid "Do you accept the UTBM usage terms?"
msgstr "Acceptez-vous les termes de la licence d'utilisation UTBM ?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2019.templates:2001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2021.templates:2001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2025.templates:2001
#: ../tex-templates-utbm-phdthesis.templates:2001
msgid ""
"In order to install this extension, you must accept the terms of the Usage "
"Agreement for the UTBM templates. If you do not accept, the installation "
"will be cancelled."
msgstr ""
"Pour installer ce patron, vous devez accepter les termes de la licence "
"d'utilisation pour les patrons de l'UTBM. Si vous ne les acceptez par, "
"l'installation sera annulée."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2019.templates:3001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2021.templates:3001
#: ../tex-templates-utbmciadreport-2025.templates:3001
